%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20merchan%20cursing%20audibly%20transcript%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ab8a9b4abc992e8c6c18f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20was%20%26quot%3Bcursing%20audibly%26quot%3B%20during%20testimony%20from%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20according%20to%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan.%3Cp%3ECourt%20trial%20transcript%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office%20alleges%20that%20Trump%20falsified%20business%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20Daniels%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20election%20to%20keep%20her%20silent%20about%20the%20sex%20%E2%80%94%20something%20Trump%20vehemently%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20private%20sidebar%20conversation%2C%20which%20was%20included%20in%20the%20trial%20transcript%20Business%20Insider%20obtained%2C%20Merchan%20also%20criticized%20Trump's%20reaction%20to%20an%20anecdote%20Daniels%20gave%20about%20smacking%20him%20on%20the%20behind%20with%20a%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversation%20that%20evening%20in%20Trump's%20hotel%20room%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20mogul%20had%20bragged%20about%20being%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20a%20recent%20financial%20magazine%2C%20Daniels%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Someone%20should%20spank%20you%20with%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20testified.%20%26quot%3B'That's%20the%20only%20interest%20I%20have%20in%20that%20magazine.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20he%20thought%20I%20would%20do%20it.%20So%2C%20he%20rolled%20it%20up%20and%20gave%20me%20the%20look%20that%20he%20dared%20me%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20now%20I%20kind%20of%20had%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20further%20prodding%20from%20prosecutor%20Susan%20Hoffinger%2C%20Daniels%20elaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp