%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20rain%20jackets%20for%20women%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20shot%20of%20women's%20rain%20jackets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a87629686a6f37bfcf75a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAny%20of%20our%20nine%20favorite%20rain%20jackets%20for%20women%20will%20keep%20you%20dry%20and%20comfortable.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch4%3EWater%20resistance%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%2024%20jackets%20in%20springtime%20and%20wore%20them%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%20each%20time%20it%20rained.%20When%20it%20wasn't%20raining%2C%20we%20did%20a%20%26quot%3Bdrench%20test%26quot%3B%20where%20we%20wore%20each%20jacket%20under%20a%20showerhead%2C%20powered%20at%20light%20and%20heavy%20flows%20to%20simulate%20different%20rain%20storms.%20During%20the%20shower%20test%2C%20we%20checked%20whether%20our%20clothes%20underneath%20got%20wet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%3EComfort%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20testers%20wore%20each%20rain%20jacket%20out%20in%20the%20world%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20to%20assess%20each%20one's%20comfort.%20We%20looked%20for%20overall%20fit%20of%20the%20jacket%2C%20range%20of%20motion%20in%20the%20arms%20and%20hips%20(particularly%20when%20fully%20zipped%20up)%2C%20and%20how%20comfortable%20the%20jacket%20felt%20on%20the%20body%20after%2030%20minutes%20to%20a%20few%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20rain%20jackets%20that%20could%20be%20worn%20running%2C%20walking%2C%20or%20hiking%2C%20we%20wore%20them%20on%20moderately-intense%20activities%20to%20assess%20how%20breathable%20each%20was%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20how%20comfortable%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%3EWeight%20and%20durability%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20factors%20are%20a%20bit%20personal%3A%20Some%20people%20prefer%20a%20barely-there%2C%20lightw