r-no-deal-island-renewed-season-2-nbc-1235994883%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdeal-or-no-deal-island-renewed-season-2-nbc-1235994883%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eric%20Schmidt%20says%20China%20trails%20behind%20the%20US%20in%20AI%20for%20these%204%20reasons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20Schmidt%20portrait%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a638610dfcda40967a6ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESince%20leaving%20Google%2C%20Eric%20Schmidt%20has%20invested%20in%20tech%20and%20AI%20firms%20like%20Anthropic.%20%3Cp%3EChristian%20Marquardt%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20said%20the%20US%20is%20%26quot%3Bway%20ahead%20of%20China%26quot%3B%20in%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESchmidt%20cited%20chip%20shortages%20and%20more%20English%20language%20material%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20said%20China's%20reduced%20funding%20and%20focus%20on%20for-profit%20apps%20are%20barriers%20to%20its%20advancement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20thinks%20the%20US%20is%20%26quot%3Bway%20ahead%20of%20China%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20we%20are%20well%20ahead%2C%20two%20or%20three%20years%20probably%20of%20China%2C%20which%20in%20my%20world%20is%20an%20eternity%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2024-05-07%2Fschmidt-says-he-considered-buying-tiktok%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20in%20pretty%20good%20shape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20served%20as%20Google's%20CEO%20from%202001%20until%202011%20and%20remained%20its%20chairman%20until%202015.%20Following%20his%20departure%2C%20Schmidt%20has%20invested%20in%20various%20AI%20companies%2C%20including%20Anthropic.%20He%20also%20became%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20Innovation%20Board%20in%202016%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nscai.gov%2F2021%2F09%2F23%2Fnscai-to-sunset-in-october%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echaired%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20National%20Security%20Commission%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20the%20US%20stands%20to%20be%20the%20clear%20winner%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it%20doesn't%20screw%20up%20its%20lead.%20Since%20China%20is%20focused%20on%20dominating%20certain%20industries%2C%20the%20US%20needs%20to%20compete%20with%20them%20and%20win%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-government-approves-more-ai-models-rivals-us-report-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20China%20had%20approved%20over%2040%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20models%20in%20a%20six-month%20period%2C%20including%2014%20new%20Large%20Language%20Models%20approved%20for%20public%20use%20in%20a%20week%20span.%20Baidu%2C%20a%20search%20engine%20giant%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BChina's%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20leading%20the%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20talked%20about%20four%20factors%20that%20contributed%20to%20his%20view%20that%20China%20is%20behind%20in%20the%20AI%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae9c3877-765e-45a6-b550-e09977fe192f%5C%22%3EChip%20shortages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20because%20of%20chips%26quot%3B%20and%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Schmidt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F05%2F07%2Fwatch-cnbcas-full-interview-with-former-google-executive-chairman-and-ceo-eric-schmidt.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20set%20back%20by%20the%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20administrations%20restricting%20access%20to%20high-speed%20chips%2C%20particularly%20Nvidia%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20certainly%20angry%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chips%20serve%20as%20a%20crucial%20component%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20scale%20AI.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-tech-cold-war-everything-that-has-happened-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech-related%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20resulted%20in%20a%20push%20from%20the%20government%20to%20produce%20semiconductors%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20November%202023%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20implemented%20the%20Advanced%20Computing%20Chips%20Rule%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20China%20to%20import%20advanced%20AI%20chips%20from%20American%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-is-firing-back-again-in-china-chip-semiconductor-wars-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%20administration%20most%20recently%20considered%3C%2Fa%3E%20imposing%20sanctions%20on%20several%20Chinese%20semiconductor%20firms%20linked%20to%20Huawei%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa88c71d-9aa6-4299-a800-6c2e77fd1503%5C%22%3ESchmidt%20thinks%20there's%20less%20Chinese%20material%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20with%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20also%20said%20in%20the%20CNBC%20interview%20that%20there's%20not%20as%20much%20Chinese%20material%20available%20to%20train%20large%20language%20models.%20Since%20English%20dominates%20the%20internet%2C%20research%20papers%2C%20and%20books%20that%20large%20language%20models%20train%20on%2C%20he%20believes%20English%20provides%20a%20larger%20pool%2