20a%20human%20being%20two%20hours%2C%20now%20there's%20an%20AI%20solution%20to%20do%20it%20in%20much%20faster%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20able%20to%20respond%20faster%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20bad%20guys%20faster%20with%20interesting%20transformational%20technology.%20We're%20able%20to%20move%20so%20much%20faster%20and%20do%20more%20with%20limited%20resources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20several%20cybersecurity%20professionals%20who%20attended%20the%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frsa-ceo-rohit-ghai-navigating-5g-cybersecurity-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERSA%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20in%20San%20Francisco%20about%20how%20generative%20AI%20is%20increasingly%20used%20in%20cybersecurity%20for%205G%20devices%20and%20networks.%20They%20said%20that%20while%205G%20networks%20have%20higher%20security%20standards%2C%20attacks%20could%20still%20come%20from%20identity%20breaches%20of%20accounts%20or%20devices%20connected%20to%20those%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20risks%20you%20perceive%20when%20you%20implement%205G%20solutions%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20in%20good%20shape%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shaun%20McAlmont%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20cybersecurity-awareness-training%20company%20Ninjio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5693285-b863-431e-b794-a5dcd40a41c0%5C%22%3EAccelerating%20cybersecurity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20can%20speed%20up%20more%20routine%20security%20processes%20and%20free%20up%20resources%2C%20helping%20cybersecurity%20professionals%20increase%20productivity%20and%20make%20decisions%20faster.%20Things%20like%20the%20design%20and%20architecture%20of%20a%205G%20application%2C%20generating%20code%20samples%2C%20conducting%20tests%2C%20and%20speeding%20up%20authentication%20can%20be%20automated.%20It%20can%20also%20prevent%20attacks%20by%20helping%20to%20configure%20and%20manage%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20distinct%20benefit%20for%20organizations%20where%20we%20may%20leverage%20AI%20for%20improving%20network%20quality%2C%20improving%20security%2C%20and%20network%20healing%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Novak%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20cybersecurity%20consulting%20at%20Verizon%20Business%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20opportunities%20for%20AI%20to%20help%20us%20analyze%20network%20traffic%20flows%20in%20real%20time%2C%20recognize%20where%20there%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20and%20ensure%20little%20to%20no%20impact%20to%20network%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20also%20help%205G%20users%20monitor%20their%20security%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20services%20they%20connect%20to%20have%20the%20appropriate%20certifications%20and%20authorizations%20for%20transferring%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20language%20models%20can%20help%20mitigate%20security%20threats%20by%20identifying%20suspicious%20patterns%20in%20traffic%20and%20unusual%20attempts%20to%20enter%20the%20network.%20Because%20AI%20can%20process%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20data%20about%20malicious%20threats%2C%20it%20can%20help%20isolate%20them%20before%20they%20spread%20further.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20can%20triage%20malware%20and%20other%20threats%2C%20making%20sense%20of%20complex%20attack-path%20data%20and%20automating%20threat%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdge-protection%20tools%20powered%20by%20AI%20can%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20layer%20of%20defense%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20deal%20with%20mass%20data%2C%20David%20Aviv%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20Radware%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetitors%20that%20didn't%20adopt%20those%20machine-learning%20technologies%20have%20gotten%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Wilson%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexabeam-ceo-handled-covid19-four-sick-employees-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExabeam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20network%20security%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b84898c-98d6-47be-91d0-f45686ed332b%5C%22%3E5G%20to%20strengthen%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E5G%20can%20also%20boost%20the%20capabilities%20of%20AI%20applications%20themselves.%20With%205G%2C%20AI%20can%20do%20more%20computation%20and%20sensor%20analysis%20on%20the%20edge%2C%20meaning%20the%20computation%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20data%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20of%20AI%20and%205G%20will%20make%20it%20inevitable%20that%20we%20will%20be%20using%20machines%20for%20tasks%20that%20are%20currently%20performed%20by%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ev%20Kontsevoy%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Teleport%2C%20an%20identity%20access%20and%20management%20software%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20for%20companies%20to%20apply%20AI%20to%20their%20cybersecurity%20practices%20because%20humans%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20up%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frsa-president-cybersecurity-break-with-dell-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERohit%20Ghai%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20CEO%20of%20RSA%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%205G%20network%20is%20very%20very%20dynamic%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghai%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20changing%20all%20the%20time.%20Human%20approaches%20to%20securing%20that%20are%20not%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20dynamic%20nature%20of%20the%20network.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20mobile%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiot-infrastructure-technology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20of%20Things%3C%2Fa%3E%20devices%20have%20become%20more%20ubiquitous%2C%20they're%20using%20even%20more%20data%2C%20which%20generative%20AI%20can%20help%20filter%20and%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20required%20to%20collect%20an%20or