Canada%20and%20expect%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20responsibilities%20without%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInflammatory%20speeches%20were%20delivered%20by%20Dal%20Khalsa's%20Paramjit%20Mand%20and%20Avtar%20Singh%20Pannu%2C%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Indian%20security%20agencies%2C%20at%20the%20six-km%20Nagar%20Kirtan%20organised%20at%20Malton%20in%20Canada%20on%20Sunday.%20One%20of%20the%20floats%20displayed%20a%20map%20of%20Khalistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20are%20aware%2C%20we%20have%20repeatedly%20raised%20our%20strong%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20violent%20imagery%20being%20used%20by%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%20against%20our%20political%20leadership.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%20float%20depicting%20the%20assassination%20of%20our%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20used%20in%20a%20procession%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20again%20call%20upon%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20to%20stop%20providing%20criminal%20and%20secessionist%20elements%20a%20safe%20haven%20and%20political%20space%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20following%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20in%20September%20last%20year%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%2045-year-old%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Khalistan%20separatist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20dismissed%20Trudeau's%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20groups%20in%20Canada%20has%20long%20frustrated%20India%2C%20which%20had%20designated%20Nijjar%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20three%20Indian%20nationals%20last%20week%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%2C%20police%20in%20Canada%20said%20they%20had%20worked%20with%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20without%20giving%20additional%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20arrests%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20Canada%20has%20been%20issuing%20visas%20to%20people%20with%20links%20to%20organised%20crime%20despite%20warnings%20from%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20countries%2C%20these%20kinds%20of%20people%20have%20organised%20themselves%20politically%20and%20become%20a%20political%20lobby%20and%20in%20some%20of%20these%20democratic%20countries%2C%20the%20politicians%20of%20these%20countries%20are%20made%20to%20believe%20that%20if%20they%20defer%20to%20these%20people%20or%20pander%20to%20these%20people%2C%20these%20people%20have%20some%20ability%20to%20get%20a%20community%20to%20support%20them.%20So%2C%20they%20have%20tried%20to%20create%20space%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20these%20countries.%20I%20mean%2C%20at%20this%20time%2C%20it's%20not%20so%20much%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20last%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715101020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F122o7v0g_modi-trudeau-afp_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fglorification-of-violence-india-slams-canada-over-khalistani-floats-5611239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20on%20Tuesday%20again%20hit%20out%20at%20Canada%20over%20a%20parade%20by%20Ontario%20Gurdwara%20Committee%20that%20raised%20separatist%20slogans%20and%20floats%2C%20urging%20Ottawa%20to%20%26quot%3Bstop%20providing%20criminal%20and%20