o%20Exercise%20By%20Teacher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20incident%2C%20a%20Chinese%20college%20student%20with%20heart%20disease%20died%20after%20being%20forced%20by%20her%20teacher%20to%20take%20part%20in%20sports%20activities%2C%20as%20per%20her%20family.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3259578%2Fchina-teenager-dies-heart-attack-after-teacher-forces-her-exercise-insists-illness-fake-delays-first%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20first-year%20student%20at%20Baicheng%20Medical%20College%20in%20northeastern%20Jilin%20province%20experienced%20the%20seizure%20on%20April%2012%20while%20out%20for%20a%20run%20with%20her%20classmates.%20After%20being%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20teenager%20with%20the%20last%20name%20Zhao%20died%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%2C%20her%20aunt%2C%20submitted%20medical%20documents%20to%20prove%20her%20heart%20problem%20to%20the%20college%20in%202023%20and%20was%20allowed%20an%20exclusion%20from%20sporting%20activities.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20the%20teen's%20aunt%2C%20her%20tutor%20Song%2C%20told%20her%20to%20start%20jogging%20because%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Btargeting%26quot%3B%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20Song's%20dissatisfaction%20with%20her%20niece%20was%20caused%20by%20an%20incident%20at%20the%20start%20of%20April%20in%20which%20he%20suggested%20that%20Zhao%20should%20offer%20his%20wife%20some%20live%20fish%20as%20a%20gift.%20The%20teen%20placed%20an%20online%20order%20for%20the%20same%20but%20the%20fish%20came%20dead.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20teacher%20also%20removed%20Zhao%20from%20the%20position%20of%20class%20monitor.%20%26quot%3BThe%20teacher%20was%20angry%20and%20made%20everything%20difficult%20for%20our%20kid.%20He%20said%20her%20heart%20disease%20document%20was%20fake.%20So%20she%20must%20run%20every%20day%2C%26quot%