g%20the%20time%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20as%20an%20undertrial.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20woman%20over%20the%20fake%20case%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20real%20victims%20have%20to%20suffer%20due%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20such%20women.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20situation%20for%20the%20society.%20It%20is%20objectionable%20to%20use%20the%20police%20and%20the%20court%20as%20a%20medium%20to%20achieve%20one's%20objective.%20Women%20can't%20be%20allowed%20to%20attack%20the%20interests%20of%20men%20for%20unfair%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20the%20survivor%2C%20then%2015%20years%20old%2C%20filed%20a%20case%20of%20kidnap%20and%20rape%20against%20one%20Ajay%2C%20alias%20Raghav.%20Ajay%2C%2021%20years%20old%20then%2C%20worked%20with%20the%20teen's%20sister%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejagrata%3C%2Fem%3E%20company%20and%20would%20often%20visit%20their%20home.%20Soon%2C%20he%20became%20friends%20with%20the%2015-year-old%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20teen%20claimed%20Raghav%20drugged%20her%20with%20spiked%20%3Cem%3Eprasad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20took%20her%20to%20Delhi%2C%20locked%20her%20up%20in%20a%20room%2C%20and%20raped%20her.%20The%20man%20was%20jailed%20following%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20trial%20began%2C%20she%20retracted%20her%20statement%20and%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Baccused%26quot%3B%20did%20not%20kidnap%20or%20rape%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20rapped%20her%20for%20her%20false%20complaint%20and%2C%20in%20a%20historic%20judgment%2C%20sentenced%20her%20to%20prison%20and%20released%20the%20%26quot%3Baccused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20man%20would%20have%20earned%20Rs%205%2C88%2C000%20in%20the%20four%20years%20and%20five%20months%20he%20spent%20in%20jail%20as%20an%20undertrial%20had%20the%20false%20case%20not%20been%20filed%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5