out%20at%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20accusing%20them%20of%20practising%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20matriarch%20cried%20for%20the%20terrorists%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter%20of%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20attack%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Salman%20Khurshid's%20statement%20from%202012%20that%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20the%20party%20chief%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bwept%20bitterly%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20was%20shown%20images%20of%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20statements%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20crossed%20its%20halfway%20mark%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20constituencies%20that%20have%20voted%2C%20and%20hours%20after%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20accused%20him%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20promoting%20hatred%20for%20political%20gain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatching%20on%20to%20a%20claim%20by%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Maharashtra%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%20that%20one%20of%20the%20heroes%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20former%20Mumbai%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS)%20chief%20Hemant%20Karkare%2C%20was%20killed%20not%20by%20Ajmal%20Kasab%20-%20%C2%A0the%20lone%20terrorist%20behind%20the%20attack%20who%20was%20caught%20alive%20-%20but%20a%20policeman%20affiliated%20to%20the%20RSS%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Beed%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20state%20Congress%20is%20giving%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20terrorists%20involved%20in%20the%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20the%20Congress%20is%20supporting%20all%2010%20terrorists%2C%20including%20Kasab%2C%20who%20came%20from%20Pakistan.%20The%20nation%20wants%20to%20ask%20what%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20terrorists%20is%20called.%20The%20country%20has%20not%20forgotten%20when%20terrorists%20were%20welcomed%20into%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20residence%20during%20the%20Congress'%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20also%20saw%20the%20day%20when%20the%20party's%20biggest%20leader%20wept%20for%20terrorists%20killed%20during%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20INDI%20alliance%2C%20which%20wants%20to%20bring%20such%20days%20back%20to%20the%20country%2C%20should%20remember%20that%20Modi%20is%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20you%20like%20a%20rock.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20claimed%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20plans%20to%20put%20%26quot%3Bmission%20cancel%26quot%3B%20in%20motion%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20and%20will%20bring%20back%20Article%20370%2C%20roll%20back%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20the%20Triple%20Talaq%20law%20and%20even%20stop%20the%20distribution%20of%20free%20ration%20to%20the%20poor.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20up%20with%20the%20appeasement%20theme%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20another%20big%20agenda%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bcancellation%20of%26quot%3B%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20with%20the%20party%20for%2020-25%20years%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20recently%2C%20has%20made%20a%20shocking%20revelation.%20He%20said%20that%20when%20the%20court%20had%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20(in%202019)%2C%20the%20'%3Cem%3Eshahzada'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rahul%20Gandhi)%20organised%20a%20meeting%20of%20his%20key%20people%2C%20where%20he%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20overturn%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20when%20it%20forms%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20father%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20also%20ove