-26-at-17.41.31-1715051729-500x225.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-26-at-17.41.31-1715051729-768x346.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-26-at-17.41.31-1715051729-150x68.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349119%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERasik%20taking%20a%20class%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20staring%20at%20a%20big%20water%20crisis%20in%20the%20future%20and%20hydroponics%20vertical%20farming%20is%20a%20great%20solution%20for%20that.%20It%20uses%20less%20water%20and%20space%20to%20provide%20higher%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rasik.%20This%20method%20is%20a%20win-win%20for%20big%20city-dwellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%20a%20year%20of%20research%2C%20the%20farmer%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20hydroponic%20cultivation%20on%20his%20terrace%20with%20a%20modest%20setup%20of%2050%20plants.%20He%20visited%20agricultural%20universities%2C%20spoke%20to%20scientists%20to%20gain%20more%20knowledge%20about%20this%20technique.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20his%20efforts%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20results%20he%20desired.%20The%20first%20year%20was%20a%20failure%20as%20the%20crops%20didn%E2%80%99t%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20then%20went%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20table%20and%20checked%20the%20mistakes%20he%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20important%20factors%20like%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20pH%20levels.%20I%20had%20not%20purchased%20the%20instrument%20to%20measure%20the%20pH%20and%20TDS%20(total%20dissolved%20solids)%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20he%20finally%20cracked%20the%20perfect%20conditions%20and%20reaped%20the%20fruits%20of%20his%20labour%20right