%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnkush%20says%20his%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing%20legacy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20each%20other%20in%20a%20village.%20When%20villagers%20saw%20me%20struggle%20for%20my%20startup%2C%20they%20started%20throwing%20tantrums%20at%20my%20decision%20to%20quit%20a%20high-paying%20city%20job%20to%20run%20a%20saree%20shop.%20My%20family%20also%20kept%20asking%20me%20about%20my%20daily%20progress.%20I%20had%20no%20answers%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Chennai%20was%20a%20challenging%20chapter%20of%20his%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20surviving%20on%20loans%20from%20friends.%20I%20was%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20rent%20and%20survived%20on%20one%20meal%20a%20day%20to%20save%20money.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20quit%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20cry%20and%20go%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ankush%20remembered%20all%20the%20promises%20of%20an%20opulent%20life%20that%20he%20made%20to%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20find%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20Ankush%20designed%20a%20website%20for%20Deeva%20and%20listed%20the%20most%20buying%20categories%20on%20the%20homepage.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20understood%20that%20my%20customers%20were%20office-going%20women%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2025%20to%2045%20years%20who%20wanted%20to%20wear%20good%20quality%20sarees%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20by%20investing%20Rs%202%2C000%20