0as%20an%20ideal%20getaway%20where%20people%20could%20head%20to%20beat%20the%20heat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%20its%20appeal%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dimmed%20one%20bit.%20But%20while%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20landscapes%20dotted%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342428%2Fgujarat-daman-thakore-family-drives-vintage-car-from-ahmedabad-to-london-europe-road-trip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evintage%20modes%20of%20transport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20back-breaking%20ordeal%20that%20the%20hand-rickshaw-pullers%20go%20through%20every%20day%20beckons%20attention.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20what%20Sunil%20Shinde%2C%20a%20retired%20teacher%20from%20Matheran%2C%20was%20advocating%20for%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20in%20Mumbai%20for%2030%20years%2C%20Shinde%20went%20back%20home%20only%20to%20watch%20his%20friends%20engaged%20in%20pulling%20rickshaws.%20The%20contrast%20between%20their%20standards%20of%20living%20was%20evident.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20do%20something%2C%20Shinde%2C%20who%20had%20heard%20about%20e-rickshaws%20in%20Delhi%2C%20decided%20to%20pitch%20this%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20Matheran%20Municipality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20told%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20approach%20higher%20authorities.%20The%20following%20years%20were%20fraught%20with%20court%20visits%20and%20appeals%20until%20in%202022%2C%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20SC%20conceded%20to%20have%20e-rickshaws%20in%20the%20hill%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmatheran-_11zon-1714626048.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rang%20De%20along%20with%20Tisser%20is%20attempting%20to%20em