his%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20beauty%20of%20a%20hill%20station%20that%20evokes%20nostalgia%20in%20so%20many%20of%20us%20is%20preserved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20falls%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20Rang%20De%E2%80%99s%20many%20social%20undertakings.%20Started%20by%20Ram%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Smita%2C%20in%20their%20forties%20%E2%80%94%20who%20moved%20back%20to%20India%20from%20the%20UK%20in%202008%20%E2%80%94%20the%20peer-to-peer%20model%20invites%20individuals%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331030%2Fstartup-incubator-aic-isb-creating-impact-with-innovative-solutions-for-founders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvest%20in%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20artisans%2C%20entrepreneurs%20and%20small%20business%20owners%20from%20rural%20communities.%20People%20can%20choose%20to%20invest%20as%20much%20as%20Rs%20100%20or%20more%20into%20a%20state%2C%20fund%20or%20individual%20of%20their%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20better%3F%20The%20loan%20is%20transferred%20to%20the%20investee%E2%80%99s%20account%20and%20is%20repaid%20with%20interest!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20an%20e-rickshaw%20and%20help%20hand%20rickshaw%20pullers%20today!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvest%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frangde.in%2Ffund%2Fmatheranerickshawfund%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBankers%20to%20the%20underbanked%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20the%20world%20erupted%20with%20admiration%20for%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20for%20Peace.%20Known%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbanker%20to%20the%20poor%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20was%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20revolutionary%20microcredit%20system%20that%20earned%20him%20the%20moniker.%20According%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20endeavour%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20extended%20credit%20to%20more%20than%20seven%20million%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20poor%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20the%20significance%20of%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20work%20is%20that%20the%20people%20he%20helped%20are%20those%20that%20traditional%20banks%20turned%20their%20backs%20on.%20A%20high%20risk%20of%20default%2C%20coupled%20with%20lending%20tiny%20loans%20at%20reasonable%20interest%2C%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20banks%E2%80%99%20reluctance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20way%20Yunus%20saw%20it%2C%20all%20these%20people%20needed%20was%20a%20chance.%20And%20so%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20on%20to%20start%20a%20full-fledged%20bank%20for%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20poor%2C%20The%20Grameen%20Bank%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20poor%20as%20creditworthy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20of%20this%20internationally-acclaimed%20model%20made%20it%20to%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20book%20%E2%80%98Creating%20a%20World%20Without%20Poverty%E2%80%99.%20And%20when%20Ram%20laid%20hands%20on%20it%20in%202006%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20put%20it%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Little%20Data%20Book%20on%20Financial%20Inclusion%202022%20(a%20pocket%20edition%20of%20the%20Global%20Findex%20Database)%2C%20India%20is%20behind%20Bangladesh%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CAdd%20to%20this%20the%20high%20rate%20of%20interest%20and