%20guests%2C%20who%20flock%20there%2C%20raving%20about%20the%20homestay%2C%20is%20music%20to%20Kavita%20and%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20ears%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%20The%20land%20has%20almost%20been%20like%20their%20baby%3B%20one%20that%20has%20grown%20up%20with%20Devaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20entrepreneurship%20along%20the%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooms%20at%20Parijaat%20Goa%20homestay%20exude%20traditional%20architecture%20and%20cultural%20influences%20of%20Kerala%20heritage%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-2-1714390734-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348533%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooms%20at%20Parijaat%20Goa%20homestay%20exude%20traditional%20architecture%20and%20cultural%20influences%20of%20Kerala%20heritage%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Kavita%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhomestay-3-1714390853.jpg%5C%22%20wi