20crossing%2040%20degrees%20Celcius%20in%20many%20cities%2C%20leading%20to%20severe%20dehydration.%20Doctors%20typically%20recommend%20an%20Oral%20Rehydration%20Salts%20(ORS)%20solution%20for%20diarrhoea%20and%20dehydration%2C%20especially%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfants%20and%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Indian%20households%20are%20stocked%20up%20with%20packets%20of%20ORS%20solutions%2C%20and%20use%20them%20to%20beat%20the%20heat%2C%20also%20using%20it%20for%20children.%20Pharmacies%20are%20also%20stocked%20up%20with%20ORS%20solutions%20from%20different%20brands%2C%20available%20in%20different%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20bone%20of%20contention%20here%20is%2C%20are%20these%20real%20ORS%20solutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ORS%20solution%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20into%20identifying%20what%E2%80%99s%20real%20and%20not%2C%20we%20first%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20purpose%20behind%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20life-saving%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20diarrhoea%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20in%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20Deaths%20due%20to%20diarrhoea%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoccur%20due%20to%20dehydration%2C%20which%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20giving%20fluids%20at%20home%2C%20and%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20ORS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EORS%20is%20a%20mixture%20of%20salt%20and%20sugar%20dissolved%20in%20water%20that%20can%20treat%20dehydration%20caused%20by%20diarrhoea%2C%20heat%20stroke%20or%20other%20illnesses%20where%20you%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20fluid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsed%20since%201969%20by%20the%20WHO%20and%20UNICEF%2C%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20treatments%20for%20clinical%20dehydration%20across%20the%20world%2C%20which%20is%20cheap%20on%20the%20pocket%20too.%20It%20is%20recommended%20to%20treat%20dehydration%20across%20all%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EORS%2C%20a%20balanced%20glucose-electrolyte%20mixture%2C%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20solution%20and%20is%20NOT%20the%20name%20of%20a%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20identify%20fake%20ORS%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20news%20reports%20and%20warnings%20by%20the%20FSSAI%20to%20companies%20to%20stop%20printing%20misleading%20labels%20on%20energy%20drinks%20and%20calling%20them%20ORS.%20Yet%2C%20it%20continues%20as%20pharmacies%20are%20filled%20with%20energy%20drinks%20packaged%20as%20the%20solution%2C%20while%20it%20is%20just%20another%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevant%20Himatsingka%2C%20a%20health%20coach%20and%20content%20creator%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20crusade%20against%20such%20mislabelling%20and%20misinformation%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20new%20video%20where%20he%20explains%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20identify%20real%20ORS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20talks%20about%20the%20issues%20with%20fake%20ORS%20%E2%80%94%20primarily%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20has%20high%20sugar%20and%20%E2%80%98dangerously%20low%20sodium%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20also%20show%20that%20energy%20drinks%20disguised%20as%20ORS%20result%20in%20worsening%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20can%20pick%20the%20right%20ORS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20correct%20ORS%20product%20will%20have%20%E2%80%98based%20on%20WHO%20formula%E2%80%99%20printed%20over%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20real%20ORS%20is%20a%20drug%2C%20the%20fake%20ORS%20is%20just%20an%20energy%20drink%20that%20is%20regulated%20by%20the%20FSSAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20ORS%20packet%20has%20an%20FSSAI%20sign%20on%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20fake.%20If%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20sign%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20real%3B%20purchase%20it!%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6V8cEtrVEV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20(%40foodpharmer)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714463533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20Indian%20households%20rely%20on%20Oral%20Rehydration%20Salts%20(ORS)%20